{color:#de350b}*Steps :*{color} 
 * Open the Web application ( [https://forkify.qa-academy.eu/#428604.56356479914] ) 
 * Place cursor on the search bar . 
 * Use Keyword of the food . [^Bug_9.mp4]

{color:#de350b}*Actual Result :* {color}

Can't find food using keyword .

{color:#de350b}*Expected Result :*{color} 

Should find food using keyword .

{color:#de350b}*Steps :*{color} 
 * Open the Web application ( [https://forkify.qa-academy.eu/#428604.56356479914] ) 
 * Click on the Add Recipe from nav-bar 
 * Filled up all the input field with Ingridents 
 * look at the ingrients [^BUI_08.png] .

{color:#de350b}*Actual Result :* {color}

All the input field looks not same when filedup ingredients .

 

{color:#de350b}*Expected Result :*{color} 

All input field should looks same when filedup ingredients .

{color:#de350b}*Steps :*{color} 
 * Open the Web application ( [https://forkify.qa-academy.eu/#428604.56356479914] ) 
 * Open a food from bookmarks .
 * Look at the recipe ingredients [^bug_07.png]

{color:#de350b}*Actual Result :* {color}

Informations are not showing in the Recipe ingredients .

 

{color:#de350b}*Expected Result :*{color} 

Should show all the information .

{color:#de350b}*Steps :*{color} 
 * Open the Web application ( [https://forkify.qa-academy.eu/#428604.56356479914] ) 
 * Open a Recipe from bookmarks
 * Changing the serving number by stepper control .
 * Stepper control is changing servings value with minute spelling . [^Bug_5.mp4]

{color:#de350b}*Actual Result :* {color}

Minutes spellings is changing when increment or decrement in Serving by stepper control.

 

{color:#de350b}*Expected Result :*{color} 

Stepper control should change servings value not other functionality or GUI

{color:#de350b}*Steps :*{color} 
