 * Click the Seach button without data . [^Bug_4.mp4]

{color:#de350b}*Actual Result :* {color}

 Loading infinite times when search without data 

 

{color:#de350b}*Expected Result :*{color} 

Should show all relevent food  or  should stop loading

{color:#de350b}*Steps :*{color} 
